{"tid":1791913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我發左個夢 希望大家入黎睇唔好屌我.","createTime":"2019-12-21T08:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T08:19:47.000Z","uid":140797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"66f2a3a16394a1dc5d012f269d8b74a9660f53f0","tid":1791913,"uid":140797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"尋晚發夢去左尚德停車場<br />\n見到周梓樂.<br />\n我同佢講 你上天啦唔好再留係人世<br />\n佢唔肯 好似等緊人幫佢申冤.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係我諗多定佢真係報夢比我...？<br />\n唔係尻吹出黎 係真係發左個禁既夢.<br />\n點都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家可唔可以唔好忘記佢同其他死左既手足.....<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4c558384cff3c3087be16e91e6de62f5f43403","tid":1791913,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}